This is working script for this project.

Put this script in /etc/init.d/

Put Server program in /usr/local/bin/
or any other directory (don't forget also change it in script file).

Register script as a start-up service (daemon):
$ sudo chmod +x /etc/init.d/Server
$ sudo update-rc.d Server defaults

That's all!

You can manage you Server by using comand like these:
$ /etc/init.d/Server
$ sudo /etc/init.d/Server stop
$ /etc/init.d/Server status
$ sudo /etc/init.d/Server start

